\hypertarget{greek-police-data-on-youth-crime-over-the-last-10-years}{%
\subsection{Greek Police Data on Youth Crime over the last 10
years}\label{greek-police-data-on-youth-crime-over-the-last-10-years}}

I have received these data upon request from the Greek Police. They came
in two Excel files, one with data batween 2014 - 2018 and the other
between 2020-2023.
